WEBVTT

00:02.101 --> 00:03.768
How about a neurosurgeon?       

00:03.835 --> 00:05.236
No, thanks. I'm in a toast mood.

00:05.304 --> 00:07.071
Salem's filling out             
a questionnaire                 

00:07.139 --> 00:08.607
for his high                    
school reunion.                 

00:08.674 --> 00:10.708
          Apparently,           
    it's a work of fiction.     

00:10.776 --> 00:13.111
     "I perform lobotomies      
    in the off-season           

00:13.178 --> 00:15.113
when I'm not playing free safety
    for the Dallas Cowboys."    

00:15.180 --> 00:16.414
     You left out the part      

00:16.481 --> 00:18.449
      where you sit around      
     and scratch your butt.     

00:18.517 --> 00:20.184
         This reunion's         
      going to be great--       

00:20.252 --> 00:21.386
seeing all my old cronies,      

00:21.454 --> 00:23.154
    pretending I know           
        about the brain.        

00:23.222 --> 00:24.889
How are you going               
to explain the fact             

00:24.957 --> 00:26.691
that you now have               
four legs, pointy ears,         

00:26.759 --> 00:28.960
    and a furry belly,          
      Mr. Convicted Felon?      

00:29.028 --> 00:30.394
I got it all figured out.       

00:30.462 --> 00:32.831
No one will care that I slipped 
  up playing the morality game  

00:32.898 --> 00:35.033
    as long as I walk           
    into that reunion           

00:35.100 --> 00:37.602
     with a gorgeous trophy     
        on my arm.              

00:37.670 --> 00:38.570
        Allow me.               

00:39.572 --> 00:42.073
(groaning)                      

00:42.141 --> 00:44.342
        (weakly):               
      I meant Susan Anton.      

